## Auth routing (guards)

| Guard | Where | Behavior |
|-------|-------|----------|
| `guestGuard` | `/`, `/sign-in`, `/login`, `/register`, `/admin/login` | Unauthenticated ‚Üí allow; authenticated ‚Üí session portal home |
| `portalMatchGuard` | `''` and `admin` lazy trees | Unauthenticated ‚Üí `/`; wrong portal ‚Üí correct portal home |

## Layout behavior (do not reimplement ad hoc)

- **Desktop:** persistent sidebar (`SidebarService.collapsed`), panel collapse/expand in brand row.
- **Collapsed desktop:** one entity icon per section on the rail; multi-item sections open flyout panel (same `_sidebar-nav-panel.scss` UI as expanded); trigger styles in flyout component only.
- **Expanded sidebar:** `sidebar__section-title` + indented `sidebar__items` with icon-centered vertical rail; active link overlaps rail with accent `border-left`.
- **Section chrome:** active title `--portal-accent-muted`, active icon `--portal-accent`; inactive muted grays.
- **Mobile (‚â§768px):** topbar hamburger ‚Üí drawer; brand shows portal suffix + close (X); flyout disabled ‚Äî full labels.
- **Main scroll:** `.portal-shell__content` (portal) or guest shell outlet area (guest).

